                        <p>
                            Founded in November 2013, 08 Consulting was born from a vision to provide clean, accurate, and actionable data for diverse research and business decision-making needs. We believe that reliable data is the cornerstone of progress and innovation, and our commitment to 100% accuracy and precision drives every aspect of our work. <br>
                            <br>
                            At 08 Consulting, our global team of expert consultants delivers cutting-edge services in data analysis, advanced statistical modeling, automation, and strategic advisory. We empower organizations worldwide to make data-informed decisions that fuel growth, optimize processes, and unlock new opportunities in the digital landscape. Our expertise spans an array of services, including:
                        </p>
